{"type":"message","id":"db9e6560","parentId":"d20a22c1","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:25:52.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"名字已经更新了\"，这似乎是在回应之前关于某个名字的更新操作。让我先检查一下记忆，看看之前发生了什么。\n\n不过从上下文来看，这是一个非常简短的消息，可能是用户在确认某件事情。我应该：\n1. 简短确认\n2. 保持在 webchat 频道回复\n\n让我简单回复确认。","thinkingSignature":"6a58ad124aeeec8970cfaeebe6f43ffe89fd5c1d871865abe193b28ce3d55c40"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，收到！🦞 有什么需要我帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":31525,"totalTokens":31660,"cost":{"input":0.0000156,"output":0.0000996,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0037829999999999995,"total":0.0038981999999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773804344048}}
